Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go...your Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what about my red cherry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be a red cherry in it,\Nor it isn't a Manhattan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.34,0:00:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! You'd better watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My business goes well\Nwhen I have this in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a jinx, a jinx!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let there still be something\Nof value left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay... It's just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's right here;\Nlike a candy store.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything\Nvaluable enough for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is fleeting. He may have been\Ntouted as a candidate for governor,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but when he and his wife\Nwere gunned down together like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, I'd better get down\Nto business...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I figure the safe must be\Nin this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What's with this chill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time\NI've felt anything so repulsive...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's in this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! What am I so scared about?\NIt's not like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your hands over your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no... He was behind me. Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because that bartender\Nforgot the cherry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and raise your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break, officer.\NI haven't taken anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the...? You're one of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, why don't you\Nput that scary thing away and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your hands on your head!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems harder to deal with\Nthan the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,L-It's the cops!\NYou fouled up, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody like you\Nwill just slow me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't follow me, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! This is just not my day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...\NI thought you looked familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the guy in the newspaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the doctor who's\Nthe "person of interest"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Councilman Springer\Nmurder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! Unlike you, I wouldn't do\Nanything senseless like killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about the killing\Nthat took place in that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea. Hurry up and get out\Nof my face, will you? So long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be\Na top-notch surgeon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My brilliant brain just came up\Nwith an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that meetings\Nhappen by chance, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All meetings between people\Nare determined beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I were destined\Nto become a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The underworld is full of people\Nwho need someone like you;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,people who want to call a doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but die because\Nthe danger is too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the management\Nto me...Heckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you into the best doctor\Nof the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd make a whole lot more\Nin the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be a billionaire\Nbefore you know it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Doctor! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know about the murders\Nin that house, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I saw the killer, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't he blond\Nand about 20 years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just tell me about that killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:06:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you if you'll team up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on the third floor\Nof this cheap apartment house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,After I set my sights\Non that councilman's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent about a month researching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when I was set to go,\Nthat guy showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When I looked in the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the councilman\Nand his wife were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured I could squeeze some money\Nout of the killer, so I followed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this proves that\Nyou're innocent in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Go phone it in to the police\Nif that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you and I can go somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and sit and talk over a drink\Nabout our dream-like future...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to see him for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a murderer, you know!\NYou'll get yourself killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he thinking?!\NI can't keep up with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not often I'll find\Na source of revenue like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I make it a rule not to\Nstick my neck out, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's another hot day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm looking for\Na certain person...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doctor, are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! He's got a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I often used to go walking\Nwith my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...along the sunflower field...\Non summer days like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:08:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, she died a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you use that gun\Nat someone's request? Some man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...? Oh... One day,\Nhe approached in a bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A blond man, about 20 years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. He had a beautiful smile,\Nthat Erich.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's Erich, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We met a few times\Nand became good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He invited me to his home...\Nto Councilman Springer's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He lived in that mansion\Nuntil recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He said they took good care of him,\Nlike a son, since about a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I had my eye on that home\Nfor a month,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never saw anybody like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They were a wonderful family.\NHere's a picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's me and the Councilman\Nand his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was something\NI just couldn't forgive them for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a bed of sunflowers\Non their property,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but he tore it up in order to\Nbuild a parking area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When I said that was\Nan awful thing to do, Erich agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You don't mean\Nyou killed them over that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Erich told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that Councilman Springer\Nhad a mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He also said this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer want to be\Na member of the Springers' family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a member of that family."\NThen he asked me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please eliminate that family."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's terrible to have a mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was\Nsomeone's mistress, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Listen...never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where the safe is,\Nin that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it's in the back of the study\Non the 2nd floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you'd better get out\Nof here fast, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know...?\NYou can erase the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like it,\Nyou can erase everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can reset your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so. You may try to forget,\Nbut you cannot erase your past!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why I thought that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I think at that time that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I could erase the past\Nby pulling this trigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why I listened\Nto his request...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I have to say. Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:10:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Dr. Tenma, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look at the message.\NIt's a message for you, from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find it in the study of that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew that you would come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Erich said,\N"Your destiny is already determined."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Good-bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the use in dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over when you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing like living,\Nright, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... You sometimes say\Nsomething worthwhile, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, sometimes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...you're after that unbelievable\Nserial killer named Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you forget about doing\Nsomething so stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and team up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... By the way, when I tried to open\Nthis door earlier, I got the chills...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you shivering for, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Look at me! Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"See how big the monster inside of me\Nhas grown, Dr. Tenma..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan is... He is enjoying himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doctor!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! Listen to me!!\NHey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I offered you a great deal.\NYou should be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised to team up\Nwith me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said I'd team up with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You need money in order\Nto run from the cops, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your client.\NHe'll take you to your patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hold on to your things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want them back,\Nyou'd better do your job, get paid,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and come to Frank's place\Non Grasten Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So long. You'd better earn all you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a really profitable business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then... Since I got an advance,\NI guess I'll have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Counselor... I brought you a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, Doctor... Hurry...\NPlease stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your axillary artery\Nhas been damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get hit by a shotgun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Hey, Doctor,\Nyou're empty-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get the surgical equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It was too dangerous in the city...\NI didn't get that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't operate on you here\Neven if I had the equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better get him to\Na proper doctor as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have done that if I could!\NHurry up and fix him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How long ago was he shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind the questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Four hours ago...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you responsible for\Nthe terrorist attack this morning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no desire\Nto treat anyone responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,for indiscriminate terrorist attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get funny! Do you realize\Nthe situation you're in now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Doc... Our friends will be\Ncoming to help us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stop the bleeding by then,\Nwill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that attitude?!\NDo you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...Counselor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This doctor has my life\Nin his hands now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If I should die...\NI want you to shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not running a charity here,\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay us back the 250,000 marks\Nwe lent you, will you, Heckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gross... I do intend\Nto pay you back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice. I'm glad you feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just break both his arms for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand! I'll pay you back! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, please wait another month...\N-In the random automatic rifle shooting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Break both legs, too.\N-by terrorists this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in Erfurt Station, witness accounts\Nhave helped police identify
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the suspects as Max Steindorf\Nand Karl Blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait... Huh?!\N-The GWE has announced
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that it will give anyone\Nwith promising leads on these two
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,a reward of 300,000 marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they were the ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NI can pay you back that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know where those guys are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll cancel out my debt to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That had better be the truth.\NOtherwise, I'll break your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true! It's true! It's absolutely true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:17:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but Tenma's there right now...\NOh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You said what I did was
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,an indiscriminate terrorist attack,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous! There was\Na good reason for what I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I've killed\Nthe president of GWE,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I could die tomorrow and I wouldn't mind.\NI feel so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Counselor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a lawyer in East Germany...\NThis guy was secretary to a politician.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Wall came down,\Nwe all lost our jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor... Can you understand\Nhow we feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Wall fell, the GWE\Nused the power of money
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to infiltrate into East Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They aggressively built factories\Non our land...one after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That is our country... I took pride\Nin shooting him. I took pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Counselor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold...so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hang on!\NOur friends will be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Our friends won't come.\NI have a feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it now! Or I'll shoot you dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll...kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die...\NI don't want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you afraid?\NAre you afraid to die?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how they all died.\NThe twelve people you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how they...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it means, to kill someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me some disinfectant\Nand a pair of scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You have that much, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Arterial bleeding... He's gone into\Nhypotensive shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I will use finger pressure on\Nthe damaged artery
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I will suture the open flesh.\NNeedle and thread...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We haven't got anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a stapler will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A stapler...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I applied first aid.\NI'm taking him to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A hospital?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?!\NIf you don't put him down, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot me if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to shoot me,\Nthen you take this guy to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down here...\NYou get out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered a while ago... I thought\NI'd seen your face somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that doctor who's wanted\Nin those serial killings, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What I did was not\Nan indiscriminate terrorist attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The guys I killed were the president\Nof GWE, his lackeys,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and his bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that there were\Nno unintended victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the girl\Nwho was at the news stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you did know about it...\NThat you had shot her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save a man like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because you were afraid you\Nwere going to be killed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes tell me you weren't afraid\Nof being killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save\Nthis indiscriminate terrorist...this killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.68,0:21:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I believed you...\NThat you were a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go!\NThe police will be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.43,0:21:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a brilliant doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happened to the money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.38,0:22:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you fixed him and just left!\N-The perpetrators of the terrorist attack
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,this morning at Erfurt Station\Nhave been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something, will you?!\N-Police anticipated strong resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems they surrendered\Nwithout a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not running\Na charity here, you... Hey...!
